title: Jose Mourinho tells Baba Rahman he is not assured of starting place in Champions League clash against Dynamo Kiev
text:
FIFA 2010   18:55 CET Jose Mourinho tells Baba Rahman he is not assured of starting place in Champions League clash against Dynamo Kiev - www.ghanasoccernet.com Baba Rahman made his Premier League debut for Chelsea on Sunday 
Ghana defender Baba Abdul Rahman has been told he is not assured of a starting place despite traveling with the Chelsea team for their Champions League match against Dynamo Kiev. 
The 21-year-old made his Premier League debut for Chelsea over the weekend in their 2-0 win over Aston Villa.
